OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FHampshire Police planned to put out a
OL,7,Fstatement challenging "disinformation"
OL,8,Fduring the trial of Henry Nowak's
OL,9,Fkiller, but were warned by the Crown
OL,10,FProsecution Service it could
OL,11,Fjeopardise the case.
OL,13,FIt is understood there had been
OL,14,Fconcern about online commentary and
OL,15,Fpotential public disorder, so
OL,16,FHampshire Police sought the CPS's
OL,17,Fviews on issuing a message telling
OL,18,Fpeople it would address questions once
OL,19,Fproceedings were complete, according
OL,20,Fto The Sunday Times.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@fO]
