CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FProsecutors advised the force that it
OL,7,Fcould risk impacting the "integrity"
OL,8,Fof the case against Vickrum Digwa.
OL,10,FMr Nowak, an 18-year-old student, was
OL,11,Fhandcuffed by police officers who
OL,12,Fignored his pleas that he had been
OL,13,Fstabbed, as he lay dying after Digwa
OL,14,Fclaimed to have been the victim of a
OL,15,Fracist attack in December last year.
OL,17,FDigwa was given a life sentence with a
OL,18,Fminimum of 21 years in prison for
OL,19,Fstabbing Mr Nowak with a ceremonial
OL,20,Fknife with a 21cm blade, which he
OL,21,Fcarried as part of his Sikh religion.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUoD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
