CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FAnger erupted after police body-worn
OL,7,Fvideo was released showing Mr Nowak
OL,8,Fbeing placed in handcuffs moments
OL,9,Fbefore he became unconscious and
OL,10,Fsubsequently died.
OL,12,FEleven people have since been charged
OL,13,Fafter violent clashes at protests
OL,14,Ffollowing the sentencing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FIt is understood the statement
OL,7,Fcontained information about the
OL,8,Fprocess of a court case, reminded
OL,9,Fpeople that nothing could be published
OL,10,Fthat could prejudice legal
OL,11,Fproceedings, and said that police
OL,12,Fwould answer questions once the trial
OL,13,Fwas complete.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FA Crown Prosecution Service
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The CPS
OL,8,Fhighlighted to the police that
OL,9,Fprotecting the integrity of the
OL,10,Fongoing trial was essential, and of
OL,11,Fthe risks of referring to any aspect
OL,12,Fof the evidence before it had been
OL,13,Fheard by the court and the case had
OL,14,Fbeen summed up by the judge to the
OL,15,Fjury.
OL,17,F"However, it was made clear that
OL,18,Fwhether a statement was released was
OL,19,Fultimately a police operational
OL,20,Fdecision."
OL,26,@oD@TOUyD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
