PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FA spokeswoman for Hampshire Police
OL,7,Ftold The Sunday Times: "Following the
OL,8,Fopening of the trial and the media
OL,9,Freporting that followed, a significant
OL,10,Famount of mis- and disinformation was
OL,11,Fcirculating online.
OL,13,F"This included requests for
OL,14,Finformation to be shared that had not
OL,15,Fbeen fully examined as part of the
OL,16,Fmurder trial.
OL,26,@oD@XOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,F"The intention of the statement was to
OL,7,Fremind the public that there were
OL,8,Fongoing legal proceedings and that the
OL,9,Flaw is clear that nothing could be
OL,10,Fpublished which could prejudice the
OL,11,Ftrial.
OL,13,F"The decision not to publish was taken
OL,14,Ffollowing advice from the CPS."
OL,16,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,17,FConduct is investigating Hampshire
OL,18,FPolice's response in Mr Nowak's case.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
