CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FMr Nowak's father Mark has said the
OL,7,Ffamily "do not want his death to be
OL,8,Fused to create further division,
OL,9,Fhatred or tension", but the police's
OL,10,Ftreatment of the student has sparked a
OL,11,Fpolitical row.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister has urged
OL,14,Fpoliticians to heed the teenager's
OL,15,Frelatives' calls not to use the case
OL,16,F"to cause disturbances" while Reform
OL,17,FUK leader Nigel Farage has been
OL,18,Fcriticised for saying people should
OL,19,Frespond with "pure, cold rage".
OL,26,@oD@HOUqD@RO]xD@AOUxD@WO]{D@NOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FWriting in The Sunday Times, Tory
OL,7,Fleader Kemi Badenoch accused police
OL,8,Fleaders of "institutional
OL,9,Fincompetence" through the training
OL,10,Fofficers are given.
OL,12,FShe said: "It is the police chiefs,
OL,13,Foperationally independent from
OL,14,Fgovernment, who must take
OL,15,Fresponsibility for letting that happen.
OL,26,@pD@LOUqD@MO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,F"I believe the issue is the training
OL,7,F(officers) are given. Well-meaning,
OL,8,Fbut totally wrong-headed, lacking in
OL,9,Fcommon sense and, possibly illegal...
OL,10,FThe problem is not institutional
OL,11,Fracism towards blacks or whites but
OL,12,Finstitutional incompetence."
OL,14,FOn Friday US vice president JD Vance
OL,15,Fsaid there should be "righteous anger"
OL,16,Fin response to the murder of Mr Nowak,
OL,17,Fwhich he partly blamed on "the mass
OL,18,Finvasion of migrants".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@ApmoD@JpntD@\O]wD@VOUwD@fO]yD@
OL,26,A[OUzD@UO]
