CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780913124
OL,3,CPolice planned intervention during
OL,4,Ctrial of Henry Nowak's killer
OL,6,FHis extraordinary comments triggered a
OL,7,Fresponse from Downing Street, which
OL,8,Fcriticised "people trying to interfere
OL,9,Fin our democracy and seeking to stir
OL,10,Fup division on our streets".
OL,12,FNo 10 has also hit out at US tech
OL,13,Fbillionaire Elon Musk, accusing him of
OL,14,Ftrying to "whip up division" after he
OL,15,Fsaid he was willing to fund a private
OL,16,Fprosecution against Hampshire Police.
OL,26,@pD@LOUrD@[O]vD@KOUvD@\O]
